      <title>油市场计信号随着欧佩克+提高供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/oil-market-gauges-signal-a-glut-is-coming-as-opec-raises-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧佩克及其盟友以急剧的早期供应增加之后，随着对全球需求的担忧变得更加急剧，欧佩克及其盟友震惊了市场，关键的石油指标正在发出较宽的余额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/oil-market-gauges-signal-a-glut-is-coming-as-opec-raises-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 04:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
